  "texts": [
    "For instance, MOSS 003 sft data (Sun et al, 2023b) incorporates user data from MOSS-002 model (Sun et al, 2023b) and generated data from GPT-3.5-Turbo.",
    "The third method involves engaging in conversations using multiple LLM agents to obtain dialogue data.",
    "CAMEL (Li et al, 2023b) introduces a \"roleplaying\" framework where LLMs generate metadata, creating 50 assistant roles and user roles for the \"AI society.\"",
    "UltraChat (Ding et al, 2023) involves the interaction of multiple ChatGPT APIs in a dialogue.",
    "It employs an LSTM (Hochreiter and Schmidhuber, 1997) to process input and output for each round, simultaneously utilizing attention mechanisms to model contextual information."
